<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<hymn_number>28</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 qiú zhǔ gěi wǒ yī kē xīn, wèi nǐ ér huó;
 pāo kāi shì shàng suǒ yǒu, bù zài sī suǒ.
 gěi wǒ lì liàng bù zhì huá jiǎo zǒu yú shèng jǐ lǐ lù;
 wú lùn zài hé shí hé fāng, yuàn zhǔ lái bǎo shǒu!</lyrics>
<title>qiú zhǔ gěi wǒ yī kē xīn 迦南28</title>
</song>